{"tid":2131514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國：國安非限制人權理據","createTime":"2020-07-30T02:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T02:30:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6e48912c55678e8377bc242928eef32d7a2158","tid":2131514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/F3ZFFP5DZLZGL7PSKY5WS5ELDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FF3ZFFP5DZLZGL7PSKY5WS5ELDA%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=f17bbcf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FF3ZFFP5DZLZGL7PSKY5WS5ELDA%2F&h=0b491a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200730/F3ZFFP5DZLZGL7PSKY5WS5ELDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n聯合國：國安非限制人權理據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SMBtrE2PLfduqfHqLLrFGO-O5wg=/640x410/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F63O4BVDB6KXND725HQTNOYXVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSMBtrE2PLfduqfHqLLrFGO-O5wg%3D%2F640x410%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF63O4BVDB6KXND725HQTNOYXVI.jpg&h=b90e3dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民權觀察發言人王浩賢指有關建議對本地法庭有參考價值。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京在港落實國安法，國際社會關注北京以此打壓人權自由，聯合國人權事務委員會昨就各國保障和平集會權利提出建議，主要針對《公約》第21條，即「和平集會之權利應予以確認」作解釋。建議列明，國家領土完整和政治獨立面對「確鑿的威脅或武力使用」時，國安可作限制集會自由理據，但和平集會則難符合有關門檻，更表明若國安問題惡化源於對人權打壓，國家安全便不能被用作進一步限制人權理據。<br />\n<br />\n港府去年10月因壓制反送中抗爭而頒佈禁蒙面法，但聯合國人權事務委員會建議，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱不應用槍械驅散集會者<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國際關注港押後立會選舉 美促如期舉行<br />\n<br />\n至於執法者使用武力，委員會建議列明催淚彈、水炮車等武器會有無差別效果，應視為驅散人群的最後手段；又指槍械並不是管制集會時的合適工具，不應用作驅散集會人群。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察發言人王浩賢形容「呢啲段落相信香港人都會有共鳴」，上述。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"7a46d2491cb6c3af0bcf8c7ac7197108ac266326","tid":2131514,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"國安問題惡化源於對人權打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8972653c3ba70acffa113257af902c27751e00","tid":2131514,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}